      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 (E46) is a driver-focused example featuring the high-strung S54 inline-six engine and a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. The engine exhibits strong compression and linear power delivery, benefiting from the precision of its Double VANOS variable valve timing and individual throttle bodies. The chassis has been maintained with an eye toward performance, including a reinforced rear subframe and refreshed suspension geometry to preserve its legendary handling characteristics. While the car shows the honest patina of a machine that has been enjoyed on the open road, the mechanical components\u2014including the limited-slip differential and cooling system\u2014remain robust, making this a prime candidate for an enthusiast seeking a visceral, analog driving experience.",
